Package: ctgPHYL
Type: Package
Title: Package for Single-cell Data Visualization and Analysis
Version: 0.99.1
Author: Carrie Minette
Maintainer: USD Biomedical Engineering <bicbioeng@gmail.com>
Description: This package streamlines the building of cell-tree visualizations from 
    single-cell phylogenetic data using a variety of existing packages for improved
    comparability and reproducibility. Currently supports tools from cellscape, mapscape, 
    and timescape, and provides a unified output format for integration with downstream 
    data analysis workflows and Cytoscape.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL(>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
